title: DC NEW 52 WEEK 96
description:
AND HERE WE ARE WITH ANOTHER DC WEEK.THIS WEEK DEBUTED NEW BOOK "TRINITY OF SIN - 

PANDORA" WHICH SERVES AS A SETUP FOR THE UPCOMING MAJOR DC EVENT - TRINITY WAR.

TITLES FOR THIS WEEK ARE:

Action Comics #22 
Batman Incorporated #12 
Batwing #22
Detective Comics #22 
Dial H #14
Earth 2 #14 
Green Arrow #22 
Green Lantern #22 
Movement #3 
Stormwatch #22
Swamp Thing #22
Trinity Of Sin Pandora #1 
Trinity Of Sin The Phantom Stranger #10

PUBLISHED BY DC

ENJOY AND SEED...

P.S. On another note,went to see Man of steel finally last night,and I must say I was
disappointed,while it had it's epic moments overall it was nothing special,I would rate it 6.5 out of 10...
